29#include <gelf.h>
30#include <libelf.h>
31
32#include "_libelf.h"
33
34__RCSID("$NetBSD: gelf_fsize.c,v 1.3 2016/02/20 02:43:42 christos Exp $");
35ELFTC_VCSID("Id: gelf_fsize.c 3174 2015-03-27 17:13:41Z emaste ");
36
37size_t
38elf32_fsize(Elf_Type t, size_t c, unsigned int v)
39{
40 return (_libelf_fsize(t, ELFCLASS32, v, c));
41}
42
43size_t
44elf64_fsize(Elf_Type t, size_t c, unsigned int v)
45{
46 return (_libelf_fsize(t, ELFCLASS64, v, c));
47}
48
49size_t
50gelf_fsize(Elf *e, Elf_Type t, size_t c, unsigned int v)
51{
52
53 if (e == NULL) {
54 LIBELF_SET_ERROR(ARGUMENT, 0);
55 return (0);
56 }
57
58 if (e->e_class == ELFCLASS32 || e->e_class == ELFCLASS64)
59 return (_libelf_fsize(t, e->e_class, v, c));
60
61 LIBELF_SET_ERROR(ARGUMENT, 0);
62 return (0);
63}
